{
  "stem": "3165.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like I say, Jewish-- Yiddish-- my father taught me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't go to school until I was seven, and the war was-- it was-- the war was broken out at that time.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember just going to school very briefly, Maybe?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just for a few months in grade one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One of my brothers was studying at the yeshiva before the war, in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But when the war broke out-- before the war broke out-- he came home.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my brothers and sisters, I guess, still were going to regular public school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In this area, before the war was very good relationship, and-- even though it was Poland, but lot of Ukrainians lived there, and Polish people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, like I say, I was only, like, six years old, but I remember they were all very friendly before the war, always helpful, and always-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they were always nice, so far as I can remember them.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Probably mostly with my brothers and sisters and just kids that would come to the store.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I remember faintly that there was some talk.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Naturally, we never had-- I don't think we even had a radio or newspapers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Communications was very limited.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I think there was talk that there's going to be a war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But nobody knew-- nobody predicted, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] you know, one like that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I had an Auntie who lived in-- I remember that time that she lived in America-- Auntie Shaindl.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And just before the war, I remember, she came to visit us shortly before, because I remember her.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was with us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was Auntie-- Mimi Shaindl from America.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Whether she wanted my family to come to the States-- whatever-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
